So there are different ways
that you can test the behavior.

5
00:00:14,380 --> 00:00:16,400
One of them is unit testing.

6
00:00:16,400 --> 00:00:20,290
So with unit testing you basically just
want to test a particular piece of code.

7
00:00:20,290 --> 00:00:24,990
So you want to make sure that you are only
testing an isolated piece of method,

8
00:00:24,990 --> 00:00:26,870
