>> And then once you're pretty sure that
that little piece of code is working

10
00:00:30,940 --> 00:00:34,290
properly, you can use
integration tests which will

11
00:00:34,290 --> 00:00:37,660
check the connection between that piece
of code and other pieces of code.

12
00:00:37,660 --> 00:00:40,880
So if you're writing a service that say,
like relies on a database,

13
00:00:40,880 --> 00:00:44,350
you can actually check the connection
between your code and the database.

14
00:00:44,350 --> 00:00:48,400
